feat(integration): ThermogenZero lex_bridge and project registration (#77, #78)

Add cross-org integration for ThermogenZero as first project in the
SynergyCarbon credit registry:

- lex_bridge.fl: FastLang circuit that receives TZ FPGA attestations via
  eStream lex_bridge, validates ML-DSA-87 witness signatures (3-of-5),
  maps to SC verification pipeline format, and publishes to
  sc.attestations.thermogenzero.raw
- project_config.yaml: TZ project registration with EPA AP-42 methane
  destruction methodology, FPGA witness node enrollment, per-site
  sub-lex mappings (Alpha/Bravo), and quarterly credit vintage config
- attestation_adapter.ts: TypeScript adapter for TZ attestation format,
  methane destruction CO2e calculations, and vintage helpers
- ESZ test fixtures for bridge validation and cross-org E2E pipeline

Closes #77, closes #78
